step_list.element_value:
My Lists
          Create
Make a new, blank list for your next shopping trip by clicking on "Add New List" or select one of our Project Starter Lists to view and get started with a pre-existing list of items for the most common household projects.
Manage
When you create a list, you can easily add a title, description, notes and a budget by clicking "Edit Information" on the list's page.

Browse the site and easily add items to any list by clicking the "Add to My List" button.

Choose "Add Free-form Item" to include a generic item to your list. Free-form items are placeholders that can be easily replaced with a specific item from MENARDS.COM®.

Click "Add Notes" or "Select" to edit information about any item on your list.

You can even easily replace the pre-existing items on Project Starter Lists by clicking the "Search" link next to the item's name.Co-Own
Collaborate on a list by co-owning it with your contractor, friend or business partner. When you're logged into your MENARDS.COM® account, you can co-own a list with anyone else who has a MENARDS.COM® account. Both owners of the list will have full editing rights of the co-owned list.

You can also easily share your list with anyone through email.Take it Anywhere
When you're logged into your MENARDS.COM® account, you can access all of your lists from any device. Take your list to the store with you using your smartphone and the Menards® mobile app. Edit your list from the comfort of your couch using your tablet. You can even print your list from your home computer. 
          
            
      Close
